version_description:
New version 3.0, blockbuster hit! Upgrade to experience now!
Brand new UI design to provide a better experience!
New: Online and offline time records of each device, helpful to find the unauthorized devices.
New: Bandwidth limit and valid duration settings of guest network.
New: Support management of USB storage files without a computer.
Optimize: WiFi accelerating, used to accelerate your WiFi speed by taping the button.
Optimize: Safety detecting, used to assess network risk and enhance system security.
More special features are waiting for you...

New supported Model: Nova
Nova:Whole Home Mesh Wi-Fi System.
Nova is powered with true Mesh technology, a set of three units covers homes up to 5,000 square feet with strong Wi-Fi signals. Smart Auto-path Selection Technology to ensure a robust wireless network and maximize a faster home internet.
